      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for FEA must be validated per 21 CFR Part 820 quality system requirements; version control and audit trail documented.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 used under an FDA-recognized quality management system. Version control records, regression test suite results, and release notes reviewed. SQA documentation meets 21 CFR Part 820 requirements. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2."
