      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs selected for validation must be directly linked to clinical performance metrics and regulatory decision criteria.",
      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in ASTM F1717 and directly correspond to the regulatory submission performance criteria. Clinical relevance established through published biomechanical literature linking construct stiffness to fusion outcomes."
    },
